program review findings normally will be open and Agreement State representatives will be invited to attend. MRB
internal deliberation regarding the overall Agreement State program rating may be closed, given the predecisional
nature of those discussions. 

C. If it is the recommendation of the MRB that NRC initiate the proceedings to terminate an Agreement, the Office of
