August 1, 1994.



Pursuant to Section 19(b)(1) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 (``Act''), 15 U.S.C. 78s(b)(1), notice is hereby
given that on June 15, 1994, the American Stock Exchange, Inc. (``Amex'' or ``Exchange'') filed with the Securities
